{"tid":1456790,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲試過另一半突然話想自己靜一排?","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:36:12.000Z","uid":110871,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"1dc629397074d8a7cf2a3c41e6bdbca48da8f9ac","tid":1456790,"uid":110871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:47:48.000Z","msg":"話說之前啱啱好我地拍咗半年，諗住果晚比驚喜佢book定枱請佢食返餐好。點知前一晚佢話唔想出嚟，話想自己一個靜吓，我問佢點解，佢話冇原因，淨係想要多d私人時間。咁冇辦法我唯有迫住cancel個booking <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我有比多d私人時間佢，但佢好明顯覆msg覆得少咗同冇咁上心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚟緊我再約佢食飯，佢又肯出，好似冇事發生咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲都試過係咁?<br />\n究竟有時另一半真係想靜一靜，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定有野暪住我? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da6ad11a205f5280d143ea8a60940c620dc984d","tid":1456790,"uid":16934,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:50:53.000Z","msg":"巴打你平時會唔會太chur住佢 令到佢無個人空間啊？如果過一排無事 試下同佢溝通下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca42b4bff99f6b452d5871a1e7e71592861df0c","tid":1456790,"uid":110871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6da6ad11a205f5280d143ea8a60940c620dc984d","tid":1456790,"uid":16934,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:50:53.000Z","msg":"巴打你平時會唔會太chur住佢 令到佢無個人空間啊？如果過一排無事 試下同佢溝通下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:05:16.000Z","msg":"我自問冇chur，係佢唔知點解突然係咁<br />\n我會多d同佢溝通 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418bd935236e8ed754da4489844dab64ff2dc296","tid":1456790,"uid":66252,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:14:24.000Z","msg":"密謀分手囉問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset